  "Description": "The CachedGoal is designed to read data from a file named 'testdata.txt' and store the content in a cache variable called \\%cachedMsg\\%. The first call to this goal will read the file and cache its content for 5 minutes. Any subsequent call within this time frame will retrieve the cached content instead of reading the file again. Finally, it outputs the cached message.",
